        <div xml:id="TK1146">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṇṭatu maṉṉu morunā ḷalarmaṉṉun </l>
<l>tiṅkaḷaip pāmpukoṇ ṭaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>It was but a single day that I looked on (my lover) but the rumour thereof has spread like the seizure of the moon by the serpent.</l>
